codex
I have the replacement route now: use a zero-fee public Balancer flashloan for `stETH`/`wstETH`, dump into Curve to trigger the same `min_dy` failure condition, then buy back repayment inventory through public Uniswap V3 liquidity. I’m replacing the brittle tiny V2-pair planner with that route and keeping the vault/strategy path probes intact.
apply patch
